HTN: T cell width on North side
HTE: T cell width on East side
ANGLE: angle grid makes with latitude line on U grid
ANGLET: angle grid makes with latitude line on T grid
fmeltt_ai_m: net surface heat flux causing melt
fmelttn_ai_m: net sfc heat flux causing melt, cat
ty_trans_submeso: T-cell mass j-transport from submesoscale param
ty_trans_nrho_submeso: T-cell j-mass transport from submesoscale param on neutral rho
kmt: number of depth levels on t-grid
kmu: number of depth levels on u-grid
sea_level: effective sea level (eta_t + patm/(rho0*g)) on T cells
sea_levelsq: square of effective sea level (eta_t + patm/(rho0*g)) on T cells
mld: mixed layer depth determined by density criteria
pme_river: mass flux of precip-evap+river via sbc (liquid, frozen, evaporation)
pme_net: precip-evap into ocean (total w/ restore + normalize)
river: mass flux of river (runoff + calving) entering ocean
runoff: mass flux of liquid river runoff entering ocean
evap: mass flux from evaporation/condensation (>0 enters ocean)
melt: water flux transferred with sea ice form/melt (>0 enters ocean)
fprec: snow falling onto ocean (>0 enters ocean)
lprec: liquid precip (including ice melt/form) into ocean (>0 enters ocean)
wfimelt: water into ocean due to ice melt (>0 enters ocean)
wfiform: water out of ocean due to ice form (>0 enters ocean)
net_sfc_heating: surface ocean heat flux coming through coupler and mass transfer
swflx: shortwave flux into ocean (>0 heats ocean)
lw_heat: longwave flux into ocean (<0 cools ocean)
sens_heat: sensible heat into ocean (<0 cools ocean)
evap_heat: latent heat flux into ocean (<0 cools ocean)
fprec_melt_heat: heat flux to melt frozen precip (<0 cools ocean)
sfc_hflux_from_runoff: heat flux (relative to 0C) from liquid river runoff
sfc_hflux_coupler: surface heat flux coming through coupler
sfc_hflux_pme: heat flux (relative to 0C) from pme transfer of water across ocean surface
frazil_3d_int_z: Vertical sum of ocn frazil heat flux over time step
pbot_t: bottom pressure on T cells [Boussinesq (volume conserving) model]
temp_global_ave: Global mean temp in liquid seawater
salt_global_ave: Global mean salt in liquid seawater
rhoave: global mean ocean in-situ density from ocean_density_mod
temp_surface_ave: Global mass weighted mean surface temp in liquid seawater
salt_surface_ave: Global mass weighted mean surface salt in liquid seawater
total_ocean_salt: total mass of salt in liquid seawater
total_ocean_heat: Total heat in the liquid ocean referenced to 0degC
total_net_sfc_heating: total ocean surface flux from coupler and mass transfer
total_ocean_pme_river: total ocean precip-evap+river via sbc (liquid, frozen, evaporation)
total_ocean_river: total liquid river water and calving ice entering ocean
total_ocean_runoff: total liquid river runoff (>0 water enters ocean)
total_ocean_calving: total water entering ocean from calving land ice
total_ocean_melt: total liquid water melted from sea ice (>0 enters ocean)
total_ocean_evap: total evaporative ocean mass flux (>0 enters ocean)
total_ocean_lprec: total liquid precip into ocean (>0 enters ocean)
total_ocean_fprec: total snow falling onto ocean (>0 enters ocean)
total_ocean_runoff_heat: total ocean heat flux from liquid river runoff
total_ocean_calving_heat: total ocean heat flux from calving land ice
total_ocean_river_heat: total heat flux into ocean from liquid+solid runoff (<0 cools ocean)
total_ocean_hflux_prec: total ocean heat flux from precip transferring water across surface
total_ocean_hflux_evap: total ocean heat flux from evap transferring water across surface
total_ocean_hflux_coupler: total surface heat flux passed through coupler
total_ocean_swflx: total shortwave flux into ocean (>0 heats ocean)
total_ocean_swflx_vis: total visible shortwave into ocean (>0 heats ocean)
total_ocean_lw_heat: total longwave flux into ocean (<0 cools ocean)
total_ocean_evap_heat: total latent heat flux into ocean (<0 cools ocean)
total_ocean_fprec_melt_heat: total heat flux to melt frozen precip (<0 cools ocean)
total_ocean_calving_melt_heat: total heat flux to melt frozen land ice (<0 cools ocean)
total_ocean_sens_heat: total sensible heat into ocean (<0 cools ocean)
bih_fric_u: Thickness and rho wghtd horz bih frict on u-zonal
bih_fric_v: Thickness and rho wghtd horz bih frict on v-merid
tx_trans_submeso: T-cell mass i-transport from submesoscale param
buoyfreq2_wt: Squared buoyancy frequency at T-cell bottom
u_dot_grad_vert_pv: 3d velocity dot product with 3d gradient of vertical piece of Ertel PV: u.grad((f+zeta)*N^2)
eta_t: surface height on T cells [Boussinesq (volume conserving) model]
uhrho_et: uhrho_et on horz face of T-cells
vhrho_nt: vhrho_nt on horz face of T-cells
temp_tendency: time tendency for tracer Conservative temperature
temp_vdiffuse_diff_cbt_conv: vert diffusion of heat due to diff_cbt_conv
frazil_3d: ocn frazil heat flux over time step
